data.description: Amazing property, this oversized split level home in the heart of Pasadena offers beautiful updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, open concept upper living area with a beautiful all seasons sunroom, three living rooms and a full bathroom, while the downstairs offers a full master bedroom, a SECOND KITCHEN!!! and a large family room a full bathroom and laundry, Fenced-In backyard with an In-Ground pool and outdoor storage shed, the house is wired for an electric vehicle charging spot as well and equipped with top of the line solar system.
